    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><strong>QMU Guidelines Exam Tips</strong></p>
<p><strong>Exam Tips - Six strategies for exam essays</strong></p>
<p><strong>Take time to choose the right questions</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Read the whole paper carefully - tick questions you can attempt</li>
<li>Check you are clear re: the key words and content you need to know. Make a final choice.</li>
<li>Check amount of marks per question. Divide the time between questions in proportion to marks – note starting times for each.</li>
</ul>]]></Value>
